    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is accepted given the deterministic static protocol and demonstrated low rate sensitivity of the titanium construct. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is accepted as sufficiently credible for the stated COU.",
